[genericglass OldFashioned] Serving Glass: Old Fashioned Chilled

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Bourbon] Jim Beam Bourbon
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient cranberry juice] Ocean Spray Cranberry Juice
1/2 oz Lime Juice
1/2 oz Grenadine
1 tsp Powder Sugar
Shake and Pour
Garnish: Orange Slice

